{"serial": "33014", "department_serial": 31, "code": "ME2035", "class": "C", "name": {"en": "Mechanisms", "ch": "機構學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Wu, Yu-Jen"], "ch": ["吳育仁"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "101"}}, {"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "101"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 49, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程教學目標主要在使學生可以瞭解機構主要的運動基本原理、與組件之間彼此的運動狀況，以及常見機構構造。\n學生可透過本課程能具有以下能力：\n1. 能夠瞭解常見機構主要構造與工作原理。\n2. 能夠透過各種不同的機構特性與應用知識，瞭解如何去使用這些機構解決運動轉換問題。\n3. 能夠以不同的方法分析、規劃以及計算機構運動，包括使用基本分析軟體。", "en": "The teaching objectives of this course are mainly to enable students to understand the basic principles of the main movement of the mechanism, the movement conditions between the components and the common structure of the mechanisms. \nStudents can have the following abilities through this course:1. Be able to understand the main structure and working principles of common mechanisms. \n2. Through various mechanism characteristics and application knowledge, understand how to use these mechanisms to solve motion conversion problems. \n3. Ability to analyze, plan and calculate the movement of the mechanism in different ways, including the use of basic analysis software."}, "outline": {"ch": "1.機件及運動對種類、應用\n2.機構自由度\n3.四連桿機構之種類及應用\n4.其它連桿機構\n5.瞬心、相對速度、凸輪及齒輪設計基礎\n6.位置分析方法\n7.速度分析方法\n8.加速度分析方法", "en": "1.Kinematic pairs\n2.Constrained Motion\n3.4-bar linkage\n4.Linkage mechanisms\n5.Cam, Gear fundamental\n6.Position analysis\n7.Velocity analysis\n8.Acceleration analysis"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Yan, Hong-Sen, Mechanisms: Theory and Applications, McGra